<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/trade-remedies-authority> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Trade Remedies Authority exists to defend the UK against unfair international trade practices. We investigate whether new trade remedies are needed to prevent injury to UK industries caused by unfair trading practices and make recommendations on appropriate measures to defend UK economic interests. Trade Remedies Authority is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Business and Trade ."@en .
